Interface DataCellFactory.FromString

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataCellFactory
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DataCellFactory.FromComplexString, DataCellFactory.FromSimpleString
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BooleanCell.BooleanCellFactory, DateAndTimeCellFactory, DenseBitVectorCell.Factory, DenseByteVectorCell.Factory, DoubleCell.DoubleCellFactory, FuzzyIntervalCell.FuzzyIntervallCellFactory, FuzzyNumberCell.FuzzyNumberCellFactory, IntCell.IntCellFactory, IntervalCell.IntervallCellFactory, LongCell.LongCellFactory, PMMLCellFactory, SparseBitVectorCell.Factory, StringCell.StringCellFactory, XMLCellFactory
    Enclosing interface:
    DataCellFactory

    public static interface DataCellFactory.FromString
extends DataCellFactory
    Factory that creates cells from strings.
    This interface is not meant for direct implementation. Implement DataCellFactory.FromSimpleString or DataCellFactory.FromComplexString instead.
    Author:
    Thorsten Meinl, KNIME.com, Zurich, Switzerland
